  "markup": "\u003Cp\u003ENeumo is committed to promoting wellness and supporting our employees. \u0022Me Days\u0022 are intended to allow employees to take two (2) days off each year to do something important to them. For example, a \u0022Me Day\u0022 might be for an anniversary, a birthday, a religious or spiritual holiday, or it may be taken simply to do something, (or nothing)\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cbr\u003EThese guidelines are not intended to be exhaustive. They are designed to assist employees by providing a framework for considering taking meaningful time for themselves. Should you require further information, contact your manager or your designated Human Resources Business Partner.\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u0026nbsp;\u003C/p\u003E"
}]]></Value>
